com.tsgrp.migration.target

Class SimpleMigrationTarget

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.target.AbstractMigrationTarget
      • com.tsgrp.migration.target.SimpleMigrationTarget
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MigrationTarget

    public class SimpleMigrationTarget
extends AbstractMigrationTarget
    The most simple of migration targets, by itself doing nothing at all except logging a few INFO messages; this is not as useless as it sounds, however, since its Listeners may indeed be quite active, or this could be used to test the Source and Map.
